{"tid":2251459,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入詳談–點解瘦削運動員都能夠跑畢馬拉松全程？(3)","createTime":"2020-10-20T22:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T12:26:51.000Z","uid":38861,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"66496d868542532fe156a746ae1d57218ef17192","tid":2251459,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T22:57:01.000Z","msg":"我們身體的肌肉能夠採納不同款式的營養以支撐其所需。而在馬拉松這種長距離跑步的運動中，脂肪及碳水化合物則為兩種最為舉足輕重的營養。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gs5S2MQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGs5S2MQ.jpg&h=c175469f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一集我們粗略計算過身體脂肪所能夠提供的卡路里，至少足夠應付4次平地馬拉松有多。<br />\n今集將會以同樣的方式剖釋身體裡頭碳水化合物能夠提供的卡路里。<br />\n<br />\n第一集:深入淺出&ndash;點解瘦削運動員都能夠跑畢馬拉松全程？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/givMmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/givMmS</a><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）當我們攝取多於身體所需的碳水化合物，它們便會以糖原(Glycogen)或者脂肪的方式儲存在身體內。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OoJ9kyy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoJ9kyy.jpg&h=247bd20e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肝臟及肌肉分別為糖原的兩大儲存位置。<br />\n<br />\n當身體血糖過低的時候，肝臟的糖原就會分解成為葡萄糖送到血液循環系統內，維持血糖水平。<br />\n<br />\n然而，肌肉的糖原只會留給自己所需，並不會供應到血液循環系統去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34bCurZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34bCurZ.jpg&h=c4d995f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖3）如圖中所見，此為身體裡頭碳水化合物所能夠提供得到的卡路里推算。肝臟糖原數值取自Ref1、2，而肌肉糖原數值取自Ref3。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yb3p0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yb3p0n.jpg&h=d7908b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖4）如圖中所見，以70kg的男人為例的話，馬拉松總消耗總卡路里(2950kcal)，身體脂肪的卡路里應付有餘，而身體碳水化合物的卡路里則非常勉強地能夠抵銷。<br />\n<br />\n但是，既然脂肪卡路里足夠提供得到馬拉松所需的話，為何我們還要深究糖原那一方面呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖5）這是因為，運動的強度，將會左右身體決定選取脂肪還是碳水化合物作肌肉能量的來源。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnoA0yM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnoA0yM.jpg&h=e0e2d59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只不過，運動的強度因人而異，如圖中所指出的例子，這個情況下又應該如何定義各自的運動強度呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖6）如何有效定義各自的運動強度，將取決於運動時候身體吸入氧氣的比率。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o400sdW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo400sdW.jpg&h=3766614a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nVO2max是一個參數，定義為每1kg每1分鐘最大吸取幾多毫升氧氣的量；<br />\n經常運動的人士， VO2max會較為高。<br />\n<br />\n實驗儀器可以得出最準確的VO2max數值，坊間的運動手錶亦都能夠量度得到。<br />\n<br />\n如圖中算式所示，。VO2max的百分比越大的話，我們便能夠定義為運動強度亦為之越大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖7）而。VO2max的數值大小，將會是身體選取脂肪還是碳水化合物作肌肉能量來源的指標（Ref4)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FepAf7k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFepAf7k.png&h=aa204bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越高。VO2max數值的話，身體便會傾向使用碳水化合物亦即是糖原。圖中兩位仁兄的情況，亦展示得到。VO2max數值對於身體新陳代謝的效果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hyWu40J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhyWu40J.jpg&h=e7b9222c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖8）現今運動學上有非常之多的說法，其中一種門派的說法是，當身體的糖原被完全耗盡的時候，身體便會出現力有不繼、不支倒地的現象，亦稱之為HITTING THE WALL。<br />\n<br />\n（圖9）從圖中可以看見，。VO2max越高的話，身體亦會更趨向使用碳水化合物(糖原)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MsJ9sr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MsJ9sr.jpg&h=4d4832af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n變相來說，如果VO2max在馬拉松期間一直處於高企的話，碳水化合物(糖原)相對上的消耗量亦會增大，引致身體糖原量完全消耗的機率大增，出現HITTING THE WALL的現象。<br />\n<br />\n（圖10）那麼，以糖原門派學說的角度來看，如何可以盡量避免HITTING THE WALL發生呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKvr7d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKvr7d9.jpg&h=fc434dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下列為其中三點：<br />\n<br />\n1.事前採用飲食管理，增大糖原儲存量。<br />\n<br />\n2.不斷進行鍛鍊，增加自身的VO2max數值，減低運動時候的。VO2max數值，誘導身體盡量使用脂肪作肌肉能源。<br />\n<br />\n3.減慢步速，減低運動時候的。VO2max數值。<br />\n<br />\n在這裡我們亦可以與第一篇首尾呼應，單憑計算體脂而忽略糖原引伸出的HITTING THE WALL問題，就是箇中計算方式的其中一個大漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QfulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=c8092486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QfulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=8c0d65ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QfulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=6e462bd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/3165600/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F3165600%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QfulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=bd058290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/3165600/</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/4771101/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F4771101%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QfulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=4277d6b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/4771101/</a><br />\nRef3:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12048325/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F12048325%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QfulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=9c171f34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12048325/</a><br />\nRef4:<a href=\"https://journals.plos.org/ploscompbiol/article?id=10.1371/journal.pcbi.1000960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.plos.org%2Fploscompbiol%2Farticle%3Fid%3D10.1371%2Fjournal.pcbi.1000960&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QfulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=42880e70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://journals.plos.org/ploscompbiol/article?id=10.1371/journal.pcbi.1000960</a>"},{"pid":"6fd40b168ed380f22f4625ad7ee1408c86f31caa","tid":2251459,"uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T22:57:42.000Z","msg":"先推為快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0b94c8359a61c8003563b3f7ae2718df1f80e9","tid":2251459,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6fd40b168ed380f22f4625ad7ee1408c86f31caa","tid":2251459,"uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T22:57:42.000Z","msg":"先推為快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T22:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a647c1a20f277a8211ecda1cc85a5b364089d53c","tid":2251459,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T23:01:15.000Z","msg":"咁減肥應該做咩強度運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a077199057577eb503c769c1e6e7d2a9fd2df13","tid":2251459,"uid":73855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T23:01:33.000Z","